WEBVTT

00:00.113 --> 00:01.312
My sweet Cassie,

00:01.337 --> 00:02.907
You finding this means
I'm gone,

00:02.932 --> 00:04.132
and for that,
I am so sorry.

00:04.157 --> 00:05.818
I didn't want you
to have this life.

00:05.843 --> 00:07.937
But destiny's not easy
to run from.

00:07.962 --> 00:09.158
Hi, I'm Diana.

00:09.159 --> 00:10.893
You seen her yet?
She got in yesterday.

00:10.894 --> 00:12.395
We're different.
You're different.

00:12.396 --> 00:15.498
You're a witch. You're a
full-blooded, 100% witch.

00:15.499 --> 00:18.201
You're here.
We have real power now.

00:18.202 --> 00:19.769
A complete circle is 6.

00:19.770 --> 00:21.204
You complete the circle.

00:21.205 --> 00:22.271
She's got the gift.

00:22.272 --> 00:24.607
You can get Cassie
to do what we need?

00:24.608 --> 00:26.809
Circle will take care of that
without even knowing it.

00:26.810 --> 00:29.679
Has Diana gotten to you about
binding the circle?

00:29.680 --> 00:32.052
Our energies are flying
everywhere, all at once,

00:32.078 --> 00:33.278
with no rhyme or reason.

00:33.350 --> 00:34.650
We need to bind the circle.

00:34.651 --> 00:36.385
Back off, Faye.

00:36.386 --> 00:38.754
No. You go away.
Aah!

00:38.755 --> 00:40.256
Faye, what did you do?

00:40.257 --> 00:42.792
If we can't control what
we feel or what we think,

00:42.793 --> 00:44.660
we're just gonna keep
hurting people.

00:44.661 --> 00:46.629
We have to
bind the circle.

00:53.437 --> 00:55.438
Lock, unlock.

00:55.439 --> 00:57.640
Lock, unlock.

00:59.843 --> 01:01.844
What happened to my magic?

01:01.845 --> 01:03.279
Could you be any louder?

01:03.280 --> 01:04.881
I can't open my locker.

01:04.882 --> 01:06.282
Did you try
the combination?

01:06.283 --> 01:09.318
Novel idea, Diana.
Why can't I do any spells?

01:09.319 --> 01:10.653
You can.

01:10.654 --> 01:12.154
I think that now that
we've bound the circle,

01:12.155 --> 01:13.656
we can only do
collective magic.

01:13.657 --> 01:14.824
Oh, you think?

01:14.825 --> 01:16.425
I never would have bound
the freakin' circle

01:16.426 --> 01:18.227
if it meant losing my power.

01:18.228 --> 01:20.429
You didn't lose
your power!

01:20.430 --> 01:21.831
According to the book, you just
have to have another member

01:21.832 --> 01:23.299
of the circle present.

01:23.300 --> 01:25.635
The more you have,
the greater your power.

01:25.636 --> 01:27.036
This sucks.

01:28.839 --> 01:31.841
Have you forgotten that
you almost killed Sally?

01:31.842 --> 01:34.710
Instead of complaining,
you should be thankful

01:34.711 --> 01:36.178
that things
are under control.

01:36.179 --> 01:38.748
And you better hope
she doesn't remember.

